11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
13 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 3-180 of Title 70, unless there
14 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
15 A. The State Department of Education shall establish and
16 maintain the Oklahoma High Dosage Tutoring Program for grades
17 kindergarten through eight.
18 B. For the purposes of this section:
19 1. “Cohort” means a student or group of students of no more
20 than five who receive subject-specific high dosage tutoring in
21 mathematics or English language arts (ELA) and are at least one-half
22 grade level behind in mathematics or ELA prior to participating in
23 the Oklahoma High Dosage Tutoring Program; and
24
